3. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with 3D meshes and their compression, which is a common topic in computer graphics.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses compression of 3D meshes, which is a common topic in multimedia applications.
5. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper proposes a novel data-dependent operator and discusses its performance compared to previous results, which is a common topic in numerical analysis.
